1. *Sekund* mu je bila dovoljna da shvati situaciju. (He only needed a second to understand the situation.)

2. Ona je bila spremna da čeka *sekund*. (She was ready to wait a second.)

3. On je nastavio da čita nakon kratke *sekunde*. (He continued to read after a brief second.)

4. Njegove ruke su se zaustavile u jednoj *sekundi*. (His hands stopped for a second.)

5. On je bio u stanju da reaguje u roku od *sekunde*. (He was able to react within a second.)

6. On je posmatrao u *sekund*. (He watched for a second.)